OL,3,CMan killed after suspected great great
OL,4,Cwhite shark attack in Western Australia
OL,6,FA man has died after being mauled by a
OL,7,Fsuspected great white shark at
OL,8,FAustralia's Rottnest Island.
OL,10,FEmergency services responded to alerts
OL,11,Fthat a 38-year-old man had been
OL,12,Fattacked in the water at around 10am
OL,13,Flocal time.
OL,15,FWestern Australia Police Sergeant
OL,16,FMichael Wear said the victim had been
OL,17,Fspearfishing with a friend when he was
OL,18,Fattacked on a coral reef.
OL,20,FThe victim was near a dive boat when
OL,21,Fhe was bitten on the legs, Wear said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
