OL,3,CMan killed after suspected great great
OL,4,Cwhite shark attack in Western Australia
OL,6,FHe was then taken by that boat to the
OL,7,Fisland, where paramedics could not
OL,8,Fresuscitate him.
OL,10,FLifeguards reported a five-meter (16-
OL,11,Ffoot) white shark had been seen in the
OL,12,Fvicinity before the attack.
OL,14,FThe state's Department of Primary
OL,15,FIndustries and Regional Development
OL,16,F(DPIRD) earlier reported the shark
OL,17,Fattack was near Geordie Bay.
