OL,3,CMan killed after suspected great great
OL,4,Cwhite shark attack in Western Australia
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA submission on SharkSmart, a Western
OL,12,FAustralia government-run site that
OL,13,Fmaps shark sightings from around the
OL,14,Fstate, reported a five-metre-long
OL,15,Fgreat white shark had been spotted off
OL,16,FGeordie Bay around the same time as
OL,17,Fthe attack.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
