OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779030723
OL,3,CMan killed after suspected great great
OL,4,Cwhite shark attack in Western Australia
OL,6,FFootage taken at the scene by ITV
OL,7,FNews's Australian partner Channel 7
OL,8,FNews showed a large emergency services
OL,9,Fresponse, with paramedics and police
OL,10,Fgathered on a dock on Rottnest Island.
OL,12,FThe island attracts both local surfers
OL,13,Fand tourists for its pristine white-
OL,14,Fsand beaches, and it is one of the few
OL,15,Fplaces in the world to see quokkas in
OL,16,Fthe wild.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
