OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779030723
OL,3,CMan killed after suspected great great
OL,4,Cwhite shark attack in Western Australia
OL,6,FThe attack was Australia's first shark
OL,7,Ffatality since January, when a 12-year-
OL,8,Fold boy died in a hospital days after
OL,9,Fhe was mauled by a bull shark in
OL,10,FSydney Harbour.
OL,12,FRottnest Island's last fatal shark
OL,13,Fattack was in 2011, in which a 32-year-
OL,14,Fold diver died.
OL,16,FAustralia has averaged more than three
OL,17,Ffatal shark attacks a year in recent
OL,18,Fdecades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
